RELEASE NOTES:

The bestselling FATE series returns with a brand new
chapter! As the hero of FATE: The Cursed King, play
through an exotic new realm full of surprises. Fight your
way through vast and varied dungeons on your quest to
break the terrible curse that threatens your home.
Customize your skills completely between magic and melee,
and recruit AI-controlled allies to fight beside you!
Brand new to the game is a party system, Facebook
features, and plenty of weapons, spells, and armor. Will
you break the curse, or will the city of Ekbatan be
forever doomed?
